work.title: De unges Sang
Song of the Young
Vi fik ej under Tidernes Tryk
The stress of years could not jade our mind

history.p: Nielsen probably composed the song in February 1909, dedicating it to his neighbour who was the founder of a gymnastic institute. The song was first published in the institute's programme in 1909 on the occasion of its twenty-fifth anniversary.
